## VS Code
/.vscode

# Large training-data tensors (71-145MB depending on run; some are individually under GitHub's
# 100MB per-file limit but are gitignored uniformly across every sim for consistency, since
# they're regenerable via dataset_generate.py, see simulation/README.md for the repro command).
# (paths below are relative to this .gitignore's directory, i.e. simulation/)
# 001-005 (single "middle of the road" preset per material) were superseded by paired
# extreme-parameter variants 001a/001b .. 005a/005b (see CLAUDE.md).
output/001a_elastic_sphere_tissue_free_fall_test_soft/GtC.pt
output/001a_elastic_sphere_tissue_free_fall_test_soft/GtF.pt
